Coq au vin Tuesday is here which is a must try dinner special @capricebistro after some amazing French happy hour “petit plates” at the bar (everyday 4-6!)

📍10 Market St, Wilmington, NC by the riverwalk
🎬You can catch this restaurant’s exterior on @thewaterfrontseries @netflix

latestPosts.caption:
Summer menu @thevinewilmington ✨
Mango mojito and creamsicle martini are so deliciously fruity, perfect for a summer evening🍹🥭
Prickly pear margarita, blueberry jalapeño spritz with crostini🫐🥑🥖
Summer salad, coconut marg and lavender lemondrop🍋💜🥥
Brussels and had to get the multi vinegar bbq flavored pulled park slider flight, this is NC 🐖
Fungio with prosciutto flatbread and truffle mac🍄‍🟫
Dessert had to be peanut butter chocolate espresso martinis🍫🥜🍸
Please do yourself a favor and try a fabulous drink here!🥂
📍25 N 3rd St, Wilmington NC

latestPosts.caption:
@sugoitaliansteakhouse fine dining and impeccable service along the river🍽️🌅
Capture of Veii (magic trick included!) and Genoa Gold cocktails💥🍸✨
Started with Parker House rolls and Filet Tartine on focaccia 🍞
Sugo Slab Bacon (if this perfection can even be classified as bacon?!) cuts so easily then absolutely melts in your mouth🥓
Veal martini, Sugo style Rigatoni alla Vodka and a stand out for me was the prime dry aged (in house) boneless ribeye (16oz!)🥩
Daiquiri di Sugo and the Ides of March with that smoke show🥃🔥
Ended with a Lemon Meringue Martini and rainbow cake🍋
📍301 N Water St, Wilmington, NC  28401 in @hotelballast

latestPosts.caption:
Summer nights fireside with an espresso martini and s’mores @concordeespressobar 🍸🔥
It’s no secret that an espresso bar is a vibe but did you know they have more than espresso drinks like blueberry margs, hibiscus @muddyriverdistillery  mojitos and if you need a sweet treat by the fire, homemade marshmallows?! 🍹🍫
S’mores kit:
Hershey’s Milk Chocolate, @hersheys Cookies and Cream, @reeses Peanut Butter Cup, Homemade Marshmallows and Graham Crackers.
Tiramisu Espresso Martini:
Vodka, Espresso, Brown Sugar Syrup, Tiramisu, Whipped Cream Topping
Early Arrival:
Vodka, Borghetti, Krupnikas, Oat Milk, Brown Sugar Syrup, Egg white 
S’mores Martini: 
Chocolate Liqueur, Vanilla Vodka, Krupnikas Spiced Honey Liqueur, Oatmilk Chocolate and Graham Cracker Rim, Toasted Marshmallow
Singapore sling: @sutlersspiritco gin @luxardousa
Hot tip-make a reservation 📱
